            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-terminal-500 rounded-full"></div>
              <h2 class="text-terminal-400 text-xl font-semibold">Insights</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-light-700 dark:text-dark-300">
              Thoughts on AI development, data science techniques, and technical
              innovations.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-light-600 dark:text-dark-400">
